#: ../../controls/scaleline.rst:44
msgid ""
"However, for the sake of this exercise, let's say you think the map viewport "
"is getting unbearably crowded. To avoid such over-crowding, you can display "
"the scale in a different location. To accomplish this, we need to first "
"create an additional element in our markup and then tell the scale control "
"to render itself within this new element."
msgstr ""
"Comunque, per gli scopi di questi esercizi, diciamo che non è plausibile "
